340
00:40:20,560 --> 00:40:24,155
Her name is Jennifer and she is my roommate.

341
00:40:24,640 --> 00:40:27,279
How is she?

342
00:40:27,720 --> 00:40:30,280
He is fantastic. All those muscles.

343
00:40:30,560 --> 00:40:32,676
Not him! Her?

344
00:40:33,320 --> 00:40:36,357
Oh, she is pretty.
She wears her hair like mine.

345
00:40:36,760 --> 00:40:39,558
You know, I have to watch her at night.
Because she walks in her sleep.

346
00:40:39,760 --> 00:40:41,239
Walks in her sleep?

347
00:40:41,560 --> 00:40:44,996
Yeah!
She gets up and she walks, like this.

348
00:40:50,000 --> 00:40:51,274
Come back.

349
00:41:00,000 --> 00:41:03,913
I have to go.

